编码助手
要实现 21st.dev 风格的动感频谱可视化，我们需要利用 Web Audio API 的 AnalyserNode 来提取音频的实时频率数据，并将其通过 Canvas 绘制出来。这种视觉效果不仅增加了科技感，还能让用户直观地“看到”音乐的节奏。

🛠️ 第一步：在 Store 中配置分析器 (Logic Layer)
我们需要从 Audio 对象中创建一个音频上下文（AudioContext），并连接一个分析器。

在 src/renderer/store/player.ts 中更新：

TypeScript
export const usePlayerStore = defineStore('player', {
  state: () => ({
    audio: new Audio(),
    analyser: null as AnalyserNode | null,
    audioContext: null as AudioContext | null,
    // ... 其他状态
  }),
  actions: {
    initVisualizer() {
      if (this.audioContext) return; // 避免重复初始化

      this.audioContext = new (window.AudioContext || (window as any).webkitAudioContext)();
      this.analyser = this.audioContext.createAnalyser();
      
      // 设置精细度，值越大，线条越密集 (必须是 2 的幂)
      this.analyser.fftSize = 256; 
      
      // 将音频源连接到分析器，再连接到输出设备
      const source = this.audioContext.createMediaElementSource(this.audio);
      source.connect(this.analyser);
      this.analyser.connect(this.audioContext.destination);
    }
  }
});
🎨 第二步：创建频谱画布组件 (View Layer)
我们将编写一个 21st.dev 风格的组件，使用 Canvas 绘制渐变色的跳动线条。

src/renderer/components/Visualizer.vue
代码段
<template>
  <div class="visualizer-container">
    <canvas ref="canvasRef" class="w-full h-32"></canvas>
  </div>
</template>

<script setup lang="ts">
import { ref, onMounted, onUnmounted } from 'vue';
import { usePlayerStore } from '../store/player';

const canvasRef = ref<HTMLCanvasElement | null>(null);
const playerStore = usePlayerStore();
let animationId: number;

const draw = () => {
  if (!canvasRef.value || !playerStore.analyser) return;

  const canvas = canvasRef.value;
  const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d')!;
  const analyser = playerStore.analyser;
  const bufferLength = analyser.frequencyBinCount;
  const dataArray = new Uint8Array(bufferLength);

  const renderFrame = () => {
    animationId = requestAnimationFrame(renderFrame);
    analyser.getByteFrequencyData(dataArray); // 获取当前频率数据

    // 清除画布
    ctx.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);

    const barWidth = (canvas.width / bufferLength) * 2.5;
    let barHeight;
    let x = 0;

    for (let i = 0; i < bufferLength; i++) {
      barHeight = dataArray[i] / 2;

      // 21st.dev 风格渐变：紫色到蓝色的科技感
      const gradient = ctx.createLinearGradient(0, canvas.height, 0, 0);
      gradient.addColorStop(0, '#6366f1'); // Indigo-500
      gradient.addColorStop(1, '#a855f7'); // Purple-500

      ctx.fillStyle = gradient;
      
      // 绘制带圆角的线条（模拟精细感）
      const roundHeight = barHeight > 5 ? barHeight : 2; // 保持最小高度
      ctx.beginPath();
      if (ctx.roundRect) {
        ctx.roundRect(x, canvas.height - roundHeight, barWidth - 2, roundHeight, 4);
      } else {
        ctx.rect(x, canvas.height - roundHeight, barWidth - 2, roundHeight);
      }
      ctx.fill();

      x += barWidth + 1;
    }
  };

  renderFrame();
};

onMounted(() => {
  // 注意：AudioContext 必须在用户交互后启动
  playerStore.initVisualizer();
  draw();
});

onUnmounted(() => {
  cancelAnimationFrame(animationId);
});
</script>

